SQL_STMT_U.val: select CRST_YEAR, CRST_MONTH, cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINVXDAYSFROINVDAT) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINV) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAPAIDINVXDAYSFROINVDAT) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAPAIDINV) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINV91120) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINV120PLUS) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINVDISPUTES) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNDUNNINGPHONECALLSD) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNDUNNINGPHONECALLSC) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNDUNNINGPHONECALLSI) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNDUNNINGLETTERSAUT) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNDUNNINGLETTERSMAN) as decimal(9,0)) from :1/CRST join :1/CLNT on :2 where CRST_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CRST_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO :3 and :4 group by CRST_YEAR, CRST_MONTH order by CRST_YEAR, CRST_MONTH for fetch only
